We need following properties in the config.xml file

1. We need xmlns:context="http://www.springframework.org/schema/context"
    http://www.springframework.org/schema/context
               http://www.springframework.org/schema/context/spring-context.xsd">

2. We need to add the tag as <context:annotation-config />
3. Add the @Autowire annotation in the top of Properties, constructor or method
4. remove the attribute autowire from config.xml
5. When the application runs, it check the @Autowired class and use the ByType autowire and put the object of dependent class.